# Ableton Smart Assistant - API Keys Template
# 
# Instructions:
# 1. Copy this file to .env: cp env.example .env
# 2. Fill in your actual API keys below
# 3. Never commit .env to git (it's in .gitignore)
#
# For Swift app: export these variables before running:
#   source .env && swift run ASAApp
# Or use: export $(cat .env | xargs) && swift run ASAApp

# OpenAI API Key (required for assistant chat and audio)
# Get your key at: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-your-openai-api-key-here

# LangGraph Server Configuration (optional)
# LANGGRAPH_SERVER_HOST=0.0.0.0
# LANGGRAPH_SERVER_PORT=8000
# OPENAI_MODEL=gpt-4o
# VISION_MODEL=gpt-4o

# LangSmith API Key (optional - only for monitoring and debugging in LangGraph Studio)
# LangSmith is used for visualizing workflow execution in LangGraph Studio
# It does NOT affect the functionality of your chat - chat works fine without it
# Get your key at: https://smith.langchain.com/settings
# LANGSMITH_API_KEY=put_your-key-here

# Optional: Other API keys for future integrations
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-your-key-here
# GOOGLE_API_KEY=your-google-key-here

